---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home" description="Property Management Australia — A turnkey end-to-end property investment solution, helping Australians build wealth through strategic property investment.">

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative bg-pma-navy overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-pma-blue rounded-full blur-3xl translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-pma-sky rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-x-1/2 translate-y-1/2"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 md:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
          Build Wealth Through<br />
          <span class="text-pma-sky">Strategic Property Investment.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-2xl">
          Property Management Australia provides a turnkey, end-to-end property investment solution — from strategy and entity setup through to finance, property selection, and ongoing management. Whether you're investing through an SMSF, trust, company, or in your own name, we coordinate the entire journey.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-pma-blue text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-pma-blue/90 transition-colors">
            Start Your Journey
            <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="/our-team" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-gray-400 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:border-white transition-colors">
            Meet the Team
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Do -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
        <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-pma-blue mx-auto mb-6"></div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-pma-navy mb-6">A Complete Property Investment Solution</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-pma-gray leading-relaxed">
          Most property advisory firms handle one piece of the puzzle. We coordinate the entire journey — so every decision works together toward your financial goals.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-pma-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-pma-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-pma-navy mb-3">Strategy & Planning</h3>
          <p class="text-pma-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">
            We start with your goals — lifestyle, retirement, wealth creation — and build a tailored property investment strategy to get you there.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-pma-sky/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-pma-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-pma-navy mb-3">Flexible Investment Structures</h3>
          <p class="text-pma-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">
            We help you invest through the right vehicle — SMSF, trust, company, or personal ownership. We have particular expertise in SMSF property investment, including setup, administration, and compliant property selection.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-pma-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-pma-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-pma-navy mb-3">End-to-End Service</h3>
          <p class="text-pma-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">
            From accounting and mortgage broking to property selection and ongoing management — we coordinate every step so nothing falls through the cracks.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Journey -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-pma-sky mb-6"></div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-pma-navy mb-6">Your Journey to Financial Independence</h2>
          <p class="text-pma-gray leading-relaxed mb-4">
            PMA exists to provide an educational platform for clients to develop sufficient resources to meet their lifestyle goals through the use of property as a wealth creation tool.
          </p>
          <p class="text-pma-gray leading-relaxed mb-6">
            As part of the FRM Consulting Group, PMA clients benefit from coordinated advice across accounting, finance, and property — a fully integrated approach that ensures your investment strategy is supported at every level.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center text-pma-blue font-medium hover:underline">
            Talk to us about your goals
            <svg class="ml-1 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-10 border border-gray-100">
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-pma-blue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-white font-bold text-sm">1</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-pma-navy">Strategy Session</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-pma-gray">Understand your goals, financial position, and risk profile</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-pma-blue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-white font-bold text-sm">2</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-pma-navy">Entity Setup & Structure</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-pma-gray">Establish the right investment vehicle — SMSF, trust, company, or personal ownership</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-pma-blue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-white font-bold text-sm">3</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-pma-navy">Finance</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-pma-gray">Understand your borrowing capacity inside and outside of super, and secure the right lending</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-pma-blue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-white font-bold text-sm">4</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-pma-navy">Property Selection</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-pma-gray">Select the right investment property aligned with your strategy and financial capacity</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-pma-blue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-white font-bold text-sm">5</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-pma-navy">Ongoing Management</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-pma-gray">Accounting, administration, and property management handled for you</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Integrated Advantage -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-pma-blue mx-auto mb-6"></div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-pma-navy mb-4">The Integrated Advantage</h2>
        <p class="text-pma-gray leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Unlike standalone property advisors, PMA operates within the FRM Consulting Group ecosystem. That means your accountant, mortgage broker, and property advisor are all working from the same playbook — coordinating across accounting, lending, and investment strategy to deliver better outcomes.
        </p>
        <a href="https://frmcg.com.au" class="inline-flex items-center text-pma-blue font-medium hover:underline text-sm">
          Learn more about FRM Consulting Group
          <svg class="ml-1 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-pma-navy">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ready to Start Building Wealth?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Whether you're exploring property investment for the first time or looking for a better-integrated approach, we're here to help.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3 bg-pma-blue text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-pma-blue/90 transition-colors">
        Get in Touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
